divs: Sighting DetailsI was waiting for my husband to return to the truck. when a light caught my eye I looked up to the southwest and seen two objects like birds but they were bright silver in color and reflecting sunlight back but they did manuvers only birds could do they were abouve the clouds and would come in and out of clouds. I was facinated and asked by husband what kind of bird can reflect like that and he had no answer other than it was like nothing he or I had ever seen befor. I didnt want to leave but was facinated by the objects but I am a traveling nurse and had a 2 hour drive ahead of me and had to go. The day was clear with few high clouds and a breeze coming out of the west about 15-20 mls hour. time was 1700 hours and was witnessed for around 5 min.

Summary: two to three silver objects moving rapid and darting back and forth in sky
